item.title: First Post!
item.description:
This is my first post on hhuie.github.io! As of right now, I am pretty much clueless about markdown. I've heard of it before, but I don't know how it works. But fear not, my dear reader, for this shall soon change! For now, this post is just here to provide a place to start.

Thanks for embarking on this journey with me.
